title: Caloric Dishwasher Heat Resistant Adhesive
description: Caloric Dishwasher Heat Resistant Adhesive ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 1 Review PartSelect Number PS11728058 Manufacturer Part Number W10841140 This is a heat-resistant adhesive for your appliance. The heat resistance allows you to stick parts such as grate feet, gaskets, and felt seals in hot areas, such as a cooktop, without compromising the integrity of the adhesive. It is white in color, and the tube is approximately 7.5 inches long.
